  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu (Advanced Seal)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 24</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, M</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You throw your advanced seal at the target, making a ranged touch attack. If hit, the seal attaches itself to the target, who must then make a save to resist a single suggestion made by you. If failed, it will follow the suggestion to the best of its ability while the technique lasts, though it automatically resists any suggestion that is directly harmful to it or strongly against its beliefs or ethics.<br><br>Once the technique ends, the advanced seal becomes a normal, blank piece of paper and falls off.</p>\n\n\n\n",
